Quality Attribute Specification Assignment 

1-  You are working in company XYZ required you to develop ticketing system for Cinema, the owner of Cinema is focusing on two things:
      a.Security system for purchase ticket using Credit Cards.
      b.The performance of booking tickets.
    Write scenarios for each requirement to get you client signature.
    
Answer: 
      a. Security
            Source           : Customers
            Stimulus         : Try to purchase ticket using Credit Cards
            Environment      : Under normal operations
            Artifact         : System
            Response         : Credit Cards being authenticated and ticket being purchased 
            Response Measure : Credit cards being authenticated or rejected within 3 seconds
            
            
      b. Performance
            Source           : Customers
            Stimulus         : Initiate Transection 
            Environment      : Under normal operations
            Artifact         : System
            Response         : Transection are proccessed
            Response Measure : With average latency of 5 seconds
